Just wanted to make a quick christmas version of de_dust2 with mr. kit\'s fantastic x-mas props.
Spent 2 hours on making this, so enjoy this quick xmas version of de_dust2.

Feel free to use this map if you have a De_dust2 server in the christmas month :D (Ofc. every other server can have it too!)

Merry Christmas everyone!

(FastDownload is recommaned due to its big filesize cause of my. kit\'s awesome x-mas models.)
